# Study Plan 2025‚Äì2027
## Mathematics + Neuroscience + Physics + Neuroengineering

**Start Date:** September 2025 | **Current Date:** January 6, 2026 | 

---

## Executive Overview

Learning tracks:

- **Mathematics Foundation** (Calculus ‚Üí Multivariable Calculus ‚Üí Differential Equations ‚Üí Advanced Mathematics)
- **Neuroscience ** (Computational & Cellular focus, advancing to BCIs)
- **Programming** (Python)
- **Physics & Neuroengineering** (Hands-on projects from circuits to brain-computer interfaces)

The plan begins with Calculus fundamentals and progressively builds toward **professional-grade neuroengineering capabilities**, with hands-on hardware projects running in parallel to theoretical studies.

---

